        "created_at": "2025-04-26T16:15:55.941Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I see where you’re coming from, and you raise valid points. At the same time, these kinds of icons have become pretty standard across many apps, and a lot of users are comfortable with them. While offering customization options could definitely benefit a smaller group of users like you, I wonder if the effort required for such granular settings would really be feasible for the developers. Maybe a middle ground could be a “minimal mode” option in the settings?</p>",
